                    Minha Instituição
                </h2>
                <hr>
                	<div class="container">
    <div class="main-body">
          <div class="row gutters-sm">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
              <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center text-center">
                    <img src="{{asset('/site/images/IMAG.jpg')}}" alt="Admin" class="rounded-circle" width="150">
